{"tid":313954,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有一種關係....","createTime":"2017-07-08T18:17:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T19:07:18.000Z","uid":28727,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5620194c133d97cf47a977cad260dc9429330eae","tid":313954,"uid":28727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T18:17:23.000Z","msg":"一生人你可以遇到好多段感情，但有一種關係你會記足一世，你身邊果個可能唔喺你嘅最愛，喺你心目中總有一個人喺無法忘記，無論你同佢喺曾經一齊過，定喺根本任何瓜葛，宜個人喺你心裡面喺咁特別，喺你心中佔有一定嘅地位。反之，可能宜個人嘅心目中，你嘅地位喺幾咁低，幾咁無價值，早已經將你喺記憶中忘記，你只不過喺係佢生命中出現過一小片刻嘅一條蟲。<br />\n<br />\n唔知喺咪得唔到嘅嘢都酸嘅。曾經你同佢行得好埋，發展到有達以上，戀人未滿嘅關係。但最終你地變成所謂嘅「朋友」，大家可能仲有互follow instagram，互like大家嘅嘢（有啲仲可能喺你自己單方面follow 同like），再次成為陌路人。雖然自己知道彼此嘅關係已經無可能再有啲咩進展。<br />\n<br />\n當收到佢嘅讚好通知，你會滿心期待，但原來只不過喺佢唔小心禁到，話就話大家仲有互follow ，但當有一日喺街撞到，你地連「hi, bye 」嘅關係都稱唔上。到個陣你就會發現，只不過喺自己一廂情願，自作多情。即使你知道宜個事實，明知道自己唔應該記起佢，但人始終喺愚蠢嘅生物，犯賤，繼續沉醉於宜一段永遠唔會有結果嘅人之中。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffca86e4da6aee8cb204e25cb9dcca8528de2fad","tid":313954,"uid":78595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T18:19:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf2074165da7cab24d1b445a17a00c67ea005ab8","tid":313954,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T18:20:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c6074b647ee1580d12723b3393b3a86e3c4e731","tid":313954,"uid":78595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T18:21:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b1c0470430d804d12390ed6a125dea8a4558bd7","tid":313954,"uid":28727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T18:22:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我前幾日都諗到呢個po名⋯<br />\n<br />\nI know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你想搵返人，但已經無任何理由去搵。"},{"pid":"abc25fa83f2e2cfe9b013645cff4db676333df02","tid":313954,"uid":78595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T18:23:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29afe650ef4b5c0f97a83653669c0ca8b82bc955","tid":313954,"uid":107300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T18:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465dbbe4dcfa53531cf0a46c9c286e4ccd688a5c","tid":313954,"uid":28727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T18:24:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我前幾日都諗到呢個po名⋯<br />\n<br />\nI know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你想搵返人，但已經無任何理由去搵。</blockquote><br />\n唔搵啦唔想搞人 佢依家生活無左我會更好<br />\n<br />\n做個最熟悉的陌生人算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n心有不甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5f03c1b4572e212cdb68824aee7e2528d24bd8","tid":313954,"uid":21837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T18:26:33.000Z","msg":"其實有個人<br />\n佢同我而家都仲係好好朋友<br />\n但係我地曾經有種戀人未滿嘅感覺<br />\nI know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dbf327174e01b5006594f521db4dc0d98fdcfec","tid":313954,"uid":21837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T18:27:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我前幾日都諗到呢個po名⋯<br />\n<br />\nI know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你想搵返人，但已經無任何理由去搵。</blockquote><br />\n唔搵啦唔想搞人 佢依家生活無左我會更好<br />\n<br />\n做個最熟悉的陌生人算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n心有不甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係<br />\n但無辦法啦<br />\n唯有眼甘甘望住佢未來同第二個人結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3fa7e44d861dd2aeb589569b33a6f9f53b36e41","tid":313954,"uid":28727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T18:30:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實有個人<br />\n佢同我而家都仲係好好朋友<br />\n但係我地曾經有種戀人未滿嘅感覺<br />\nI know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到底你同佢應該繼續咁落去 <br />\n定喺 主動出擊？<br />\n比我都淆底唔會再奢求有啲咩進展<br />\n一陣連唯一可以見嘅理由都無埋<br />\n所以都喺算吧啦 收埋自己算啦"},{"pid":"76dba5f158f6d22972dd21dc83a7431120d6f316","tid":313954,"uid":28727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T18:31:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我前幾日都諗到呢個po名⋯<br />\n<br />\nI know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你想搵返人，但已經無任何理由去搵。</blockquote><br />\n唔搵啦唔想搞人 佢依家生活無左我會更好<br />\n<br />\n做個最熟悉的陌生人算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n心有不甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係<br />\n但無辦法啦<br />\n唯有眼甘甘望住佢未來同第二個人結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n等到佢結婚 見到佢幸福 自己會過啲？"},{"pid":"8149d46213301e9be0f76454b88a3926e1317ba3","tid":313954,"uid":8318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T18:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"272dfb73e6957049458fdaea3ba112181a1c4e63","tid":313954,"uid":124677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T18:32:35.000Z","msg":"友達以上戀人未滿既感覺先係最幸福<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">分手之後朋友都無得做<br />\n我零願返翻以前同你曖昧</span></span>"},{"pid":"54fe779ea0f20c3b0e218854aa61d5c87c3eb5d7","tid":313954,"uid":78595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T18:34:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9650fc429bf2257c0a29a962dc0505c7074539a1","tid":313954,"uid":28727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T18:38:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><b